# Local-only Worker variables. Copy to .dev.vars (gitignored) — Wrangler
# loads it automatically for `wrangler dev` and values here override the dev
# `vars` in wrangler.jsonc. Never commit real secrets (AGENTS.md hard rules).
#
# No secrets are required yet: the mock-issuer configuration (AUTH_ISSUER,
# AUTH_AUDIENCE, MOCK_JWKS) ships in wrangler.jsonc dev vars because it is
# public fixture material, not a secret (see dev/mock-issuer/keys.ts).
# Override any of those here only if you are experimenting locally.
